    • Method Detail

      • parse

        HashSetArray<DMUID> parse(java.io.Reader aReader,
                        java.lang.String aLibId,
                        SourceFile aSF,
                        int aPriority,
                        boolean aUseFSCache,
                        boolean aBottomUp,
                        ZamiaProject aZPrj)
                          throws java.io.IOException
        Start parsing, both parameters are for referencing only and may be null.
        Parameters:
        reader_ - input file to parse
        lib_ - VHDL Library name the DesignUnits will be added to
        sf_ - SourceFile reference for error reporting
        bottomUp_ - if false, compiler will ignore entities and architectures that do not match the file name
        dum_ - design unit manager which gets design units and errors handed over
        Returns:
        HashSet
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
